<refnamediv><refname>immoments</refname><refpurpose>Calculate raw and central image moments.</refpurpose></refnamediv>
<refsynopsisdiv><title>Syntax</title><synopsis>moments = immoments(image)</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv><refsection><title>Parameters</title><variablelist><varlistentry><term>image</term><listitem><para>Binary or numeric 2-D image.</para></listitem></varlistentry><varlistentry><term>moments</term><listitem><para>Structure containing spatial image moments.</para></listitem></varlistentry></variablelist></refsection>
<refsection><title>Description</title><para>Returns M00, first and second raw moments, and the central moments Mu20, Mu02, and Mu11 using one-based image coordinates.</para></refsection>
<refsection><title>Examples</title><programlisting><![CDATA[
image = imread(fullpath(getIPCVpath() + "/images/opencv_smarties.png"));
image = imresize(rgb2gray(image), [120 160]);
moments = immoments(image);
disp(moments);
imshow(image);
]]></programlisting></refsection>
